{"doc":{"isMarkdown":false,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"border-bottom-style","mdn_url":"/es/docs/Web/CSS/border-bottom-style","locale":"es","native":"Español","sidebarHTML":"","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p> </p>\n\n<p>&lt;&lt; <a href=\"/es/Guía_de_referencia_de_CSS\" title=\"This is a link to an unwritten page\" class=\"page-not-created\">Volver</a></p>\n\n<p> </p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"resumen","title":"Resumen","isH3":true,"content":"<p><code>border-bottom-style</code> define el estilo de línea del borde inferior de una caja.</p>\n\n<ul>\n <li><a href=\"/es/docs/Web/CSS/initial\"><code>valor inicial</code></a>: <a href=\"/es/docs/Web/CSS/float\"><code>ninguno</code></a></li>\n <li>Se aplica a: todos los elementos</li>\n <li><a href=\"/es/docs/Web/CSS/inheritance\"><code>valor heredado</code></a>: no</li>\n <li>Porcentajes: N/A</li>\n <li>Medio: <a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/@media\"><code>visual</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n <li><a class=\"page-not-created\" title=\"La documentación acerca de este tema no ha sido escrita todavía . ¡Por favor  considera contribuir !\"><code>valor calculado</code></a>: como se especificó</li>\n</ul>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"sintaxis","title":"Sintaxis","isH3":true,"content":"<pre class=\"eval notranslate\">border-bottom-style: &lt;border-style&gt; | inherit\n</pre>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"valores","title":"Valores","isH3":true,"content":"<dl>\n <dt id=\"none\">none </dt>\n <dd>sin borde.</dd>\n <dt id=\"hidden\">hidden </dt>\n <dd>es igual a 'none', excepto en términos de resolución de conflicto para elementos de tabla.</dd>\n <dt id=\"dotted\">dotted </dt>\n <dd>series de puntos (....).</dd>\n <dt id=\"dashed\">dashed </dt>\n <dd>series de guiones cortos o pequeñas líneas (----).</dd>\n <dt id=\"solid\">solid </dt>\n <dd>línea única, recta y sólida.</dd>\n <dt id=\"double\">double </dt>\n <dd>dos líneas rectas que se suman a la cantidad de píxeles definidos como ancho de borde<code>border-width</code>.</dd>\n <dt id=\"groove\">groove </dt>\n <dd>efecto de hundido.</dd>\n <dt id=\"ridge\">ridge </dt>\n <dd>al revés de 'groove'. El borde aparece en 3D (saliendo).</dd>\n <dt id=\"inset\">inset </dt>\n <dd>hace que la caja aparezca hundida.</dd>\n <dt id=\"outset\">outset </dt>\n <dd>opuesto a 'inset'. La caja aparece en 3D (saliendo).</dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"propiedades_relacionadas","title":"Propiedades relacionadas","isH3":true,"content":"<ul>\n <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/border-left-style\"><code>border-left-style</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/border-right-style\"><code>border-right-style</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n <li><a class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\" href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/border-top-style\"><code>border-top-style</code> <small>(en-US)</small></a></li>\n <li><a href=\"/es/docs/Web/CSS/border-style\"><code>border-style</code></a></li>\n</ul>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"ejemplos","title":"Ejemplos","isH3":true,"content":"<p><a href=\"https://media.prod.mdn.mozit.cloud/samples/cssref/border.html\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">Ver El Ejemplo Vivo</a></p>\n\n<pre class=\"notranslate\">element {\n        border-bottom-size: 1px;\n        border-bottom-style: dotted;\n        border-bottom-color: #000;\n}\n</pre>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"notas","title":"Notas","isH3":true,"content":"<p>A menos que un valor <a href=\"/es/docs/Web/CSS/border-style\"><code>border-style</code></a> sea definido, el borde no aparecerá porque el valor por defecto es 'none'.</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"especificaciones","title":"Especificaciones","isH3":true,"content":"<ul>\n <li><a class=\"external\" href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/CSS21/box.html#propdef-border-bottom-style\" rel=\" noopener\">CSS 2.1</a></li>\n <li><a class=\"external\" href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/css3-background/#border-style\" rel=\" noopener\">CSS 3</a></li>\n</ul>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"compatibilidades","title":"Compatibilidades","isH3":true,"content":""}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"ver_tambi.c3.a9n","title":"Ver también","isH3":true,"content":"<p><a href=\"/es/docs/Web/CSS/border-bottom\"><code>border-bottom</code></a>, <a href=\"/es/docs/Web/CSS/border-color\"><code>border-color</code></a>, <a href=\"/es/docs/Web/CSS/border-bottom-style\" aria-current=\"page\"><code>border-bottom-style</code></a>, <a href=\"/es/docs/Web/CSS/border-bottom-width\"><code>border-bottom-width</code></a></p>\n\n<p> </p>\n\n<div class=\"noinclude\" id=\"sect1\">\n<p><span class=\"comment\">Categorías</span></p>\n<span class=\"comment\">Interwiki Languages</span></div>\n\n<p></p>"}}],"toc":[],"summary":"<< Volver","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-10-01T03:41:16.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"border-bottom-style","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"border-bottom-style","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"border-bottom-style","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"border-bottom-style","locale":"ko","native":"한국어"},{"title":"border-bottom-style","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)"}],"source":{"folder":"es/web/css/border-bottom-style","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/es/web/css/border-bottom-style/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/921c46a374ab0a9f4cc809af0370f8c412e54701","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/es/docs/Web","title":"Tecnología para desarrolladores web"},{"uri":"/es/docs/Web/CSS","title":"CSS"},{"uri":"/es/docs/Web/CSS/border-bottom-style","title":"border-bottom-style"}],"pageTitl